  * Abolish 'unsafePerformIO'.
  * Generalise buffer to minimum required length given keybindings.
* Introduce concurrency/threading to "tryHTTPS".
  * See, e.g. <https://www.haskell.org/haskellwiki/Gtk2Hs/Tutorials/ThreadedGUIs>.
